Description: collective.ptg.scrollable
        =========================
        
        scrollable display type for collective.plonetruegallery based on the scrollable jQueryTools plugin
        
        You might soon find a demo here: http://products.medialog.no/galleries/scrollable
        
        Changelog
        =========
        
        
        0.3 (2012-11-07)
        -------------------
        
        - added title and description (option) [espenmn]
        
        0.2 (2012-09-13)
        -------------------
        
        - added arrows (buttons) with 'steps', this means it is now possible to scroll by more than one. [espenmn]
        - added rewind button. [espenmn] 
        
        
        0.1 (2012-09-05)
        -------------------
        
        - Initial release
